  "text": "There are still other pathways to be considered. Some evidence suggests that XRT can result in the autophosphorylation of epidermal growth factor receptor (EGFR), independent of DNA damage [CITATION_1] . This triggers a response cascade ultimately leading to increased cell proliferation (for review see Schmidt-Ullrich et al.",
